.TH "nvmf_discovery" 9 "nvmf_discovery" "March 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvmf_discovery \- Perform fabrics discovery
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" nvmf_discovery
.BI "(struct nvme_global_ctx *ctx "  ","
.BI "struct nvmf_context *fctx "  ","
.BI "bool connect "  ","
.BI "bool force "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "ctx" 12
Global context
.IP "fctx" 12
Fabrics context
.IP "connect" 12
Whether to connect discovered subsystems
.IP "force" 12
Force discovery even if already connected
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Performs discovery for fabrics subsystems and optionally connects.
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success, or a negative error code on failure.
